      • getMapHeight

        public static int getMapHeight(int rgb)
        Gets the map height of grass land. Note: Movement to/from grass the nest area is always a cost of 1, as is movement from nest area to nest area - regardless of encumbrance. Thus, nests can always be though of as being the height of whatever grass they touch.
        Parameters:
        rgb - the rgb of the land color
        Returns:
        the map height
